---
title: Chicken Yakitori with Yakisoba Noodles and Green Beans
description: Yakitori is a favourite late-night street food in Japan, where you'll find alleys lined with charcoal grills selling skewers by the hundreds. We're marinating our chicken yakitori in a sweet garlic-soy sauce and serving them atop chewy pan-fried noodles and crunchy green beans.
